\dot{x}_{2}(t) & = & \frac{\sigma x_{1}(t-\tau)}{1+x_{1}(t-\tau)^{n}}-\gamma x_{2}(t),\label{eq:MG2}
\end{eqnarray}

\end_inset

you could implement the right hand side function as:
\end_layout

