\begin_layout Subsection*
Output
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The output-files generated by oddtool are named 
\family typewriter
t.txt
\family default
, 
\family typewriter
x.txt
\family default
 and, optionally, 
\family typewriter
f.txt
\family default
.
 They are contained in the local directory 
\family typewriter
system_name_data/
\family default
, if the system's name is specified as 
\family typewriter
name = system_name
\family default
 in the file 
\family typewriter
ODD_parameters.txt
\family default
.
 Moreover, 
\family typewriter
integrate()
\family default
 generates the files 
\family typewriter
system_name_temp/continuation_*.txt
\family default
 containing information necessary to resume the integration from the last
 calculated point.
\end_layout

